-- Azarenka Reaches U.S. Open Final With Victory Against Sharapova
-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 2012-09-07T21:27:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-07/azarenka-reaches-u-s-open-final-with-victory-against-sharapova.html
Top-seeded Victoria Azarenka of
Belarus moved into the U.S. Open women’s final with a 3-6, 6-2,
6-4 defeat of 2006 champion Maria Sharapova of Russia in a
mistake-filled semifinal today.  Azarenka will face three-time champion  Serena Williams  of
the U.S. or first-time semifinalist Sara Errani of Italy in
tomorrow’s final.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Gloster at 
 rgloster@bloomberg.net  